text: Milton Arthur Morris AO (2 April 1924 â€“ 27 February 2019) was an Australian politician. He was a member of New South Wales Parliament from 1956 to 1980 and New South Wales Minister for Transport from 1965 to 1975. He was born in Mayfield, New South Wales.
